quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,Alô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tazmamt ipbegginen
  12,2,"Ih, Nessader it id d Leqwôan, s taâôabt, amar a pfehmem"
  12,3,"Nekwni Nêekku yak tiêkayin igerzen mavi, deg wayen i k Nweêêa di Leqwôan agi, xas telliv, uqbel is, seg wid istehzan"
  12,4,"Mi inna Yusef i baba s: \"a baba! Nek wala$ mrawyan itran, iîij, akked waggur, wala$ ten knan iyi"
  12,5,"Inna: \"a mmi! Ur êekku ayen twalav i watmaten ik, ad ak andin ticeôkep. Cciîan, s tidep, d acengu n ûûeê n umdan"
  12,6,"Akka, a k Ifren Mass ik, u ak Isselmed asefru n temsal, u ad Itim l$it iS, i keçç akked twacult n Yaâqub, akken it Itam, zik, af lejdud ik: Ibôahim akked Isêaq. Mass ik, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d Uûwib"